22:41.299 --> 22:41.859
That's right. We sure are different. Okay. Was 
Brian affected by the energy crisis at all?

22:59.984 --> 23:23.443
yes i'm sure brian was affected quite seriously 
with the energy crisis because we didn't have

22:59.984 --> 23:23.443
enough gas for transportation not enough fuel for 
machinery and to run the different plants that

22:59.984 --> 23:23.443
they run by fuel and we had to consume our 
electricity that is we had to keep the temperature

22:59.984 --> 23:23.443
down turn off the lights and and things of that 
kind. And in the homes and businesses, they had to

23:24.922 --> 23:31.172
keep the temperature real low to conserve the 
electricity and all. And the energy crisis was

23:32.094 --> 23:39.846
just really a serious thing because so many people 
just never thought about what it really meant to be

23:40.805 --> 23:43.548
without it. They just never had been. Never been. 
